      "html": "<blockquote>\n<p>版本属性：内部版节点\n权限建议：仅内部/项目组可见\n对外处理：需脱敏后改写\n来源材料：品牌侧内部源档整理</p>\n</blockquote>\n<h1>品牌源档索引</h1>\n<h2>这是什么</h2>\n<p>这是 <code>品牌</code> 主轴对应的内部源档入口。</p>\n<h2>收录范围</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>商务合作与对外材料源档</li>\n<li>OpenClaw 研究稿与整编稿</li>\n<li>宣贯材料</li>\n<li>品牌侧具名案例卡</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>入口</h2>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#/doc/90_%E5%86%85%E9%83%A8%E6%BA%90%E6%A1%A3%2F10_%E5%93%81%E7%89%8C%E6%BA%90%E6%A1%A3%2F%E3%80%90%E9%9C%80%E5%86%85%E9%83%A8%E3%80%9107_%E5%95%86%E5%8A%A1%E5%90%88%E4%BD%9C%E6%BA%90%E6%A1%A3_2026%E4%BA%9A%E9%9D%A2%E5%95%86%E5%8A%A1%E5%90%88%E4%BD%9C%E6%89%8B%E5%86%8C\">【需内部】商务合作源档：2026亚面商务合作手册</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#/doc/90_%E5%86%85%E9%83%A8%E6%BA%90%E6%A1%A3%2F10_%E5%93%81%E7%89%8C%E6%BA%90%E6%A1%A3%2F%E3%80%90%E9%9C%80%E5%86%85%E9%83%A8%E3%80%9108_OpenClaw%E7%A0%94%E7%A9%B6%E6%BA%90%E6%A1%A3%E6%95%B4%E7%BC%96_%E4%BA%9A%E6%B4%B2%E5%90%83%E9%9D%A2%E5%85%AC%E5%8F%B8%E5%93%81%E7%89%8C%E6%A1%88%E4%BE%8B%E7%9F%A5%E8%AF%86%E5%BA%93\">【需内部】OpenClaw 研究源档整编：亚洲吃面公司品牌案例知识库</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#/doc/90_%E5%86%85%E9%83%A8%E6%BA%90%E6%A1%A3%2F10_%E5%93%81%E7%89%8C%E6%BA%90%E6%A1%A3%2F%E3%80%90%E9%9C%80%E5%86%85%E9%83%A8%E3%80%9110_OpenClaw%E5%8E%9F%E7%A8%BF%E5%85%A8%E6%96%87_%E4%BA%9A%E6%B4%B2%E5%90%83%E9%9D%A2%E5%85%AC%E5%8F%B8%E5%93%81%E7%89%8C%E6%A1%88%E4%BE%8B%E7%9F%A5%E8%AF%86%E5%BA%93\">【需内部】OpenClaw 原稿全文：亚洲吃面公司品牌案例知识库</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#/doc/90_%E5%86%85%E9%83%A8%E6%BA%90%E6%A1%A3%2F10_%E5%93%81%E7%89%8C%E6%BA%90%E6%A1%A3%2F%E3%80%90%E9%9C%80%E5%86%85%E9%83%A8%E3%80%9112_%E5%AE%A3%E8%B4%AF%E6%9D%90%E6%96%99%E6%BA%90%E6%A1%A3_%E4%BA%9A%E9%9D%A2%E5%AE%A3%E8%B4%AF95\">【需内部】宣贯材料源档：亚面宣贯95</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#/doc/90_%E5%86%85%E9%83%A8%E6%BA%90%E6%A1%A3%2F10_%E5%93%81%E7%89%8C%E6%BA%90%E6%A1%A3%2F%E3%80%90%E9%9C%80%E5%86%85%E9%83%A8%E3%80%9151_%E6%A1%88%E4%BE%8B%E5%8D%A1_%E5%A4%AA%E4%BA%8C\">【需内部】案例卡：太二</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#/doc/90_%E5%86%85%E9%83%A8%E6%BA%90%E6%A1%A3%2F10_%E5%93%81%E7%89%8C%E6%BA%90%E6%A1%A3%2F%E3%80%90%E9%9C%80%E5%86%85%E9%83%A8%E3%80%9152_%E6%A1%88%E4%BE%8B%E5%8D%A1_%E5%B0%8F%E7%8C%AA%E6%9F%A5%E7%90%86\">【需内部】案例卡：小猪查理</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#/doc/90_%E5%86%85%E9%83%A8%E6%BA%90%E6%A1%A3%2F10_%E5%93%81%E7%89%8C%E6%BA%90%E6%A1%A3%2F%E3%80%90%E9%9C%80%E5%86%85%E9%83%A8%E3%80%9153_%E6%A1%88%E4%BE%8B%E5%8D%A1_%E9%BB%84%E8%AE%B0%E7%85%8C\">【需内部】案例卡：黄记煌</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#/doc/90_%E5%86%85%E9%83%A8%E6%BA%90%E6%A1%A3%2F10_%E5%93%81%E7%89%8C%E6%BA%90%E6%A1%A3%2F%E3%80%90%E9%9C%80%E5%86%85%E9%83%A8%E3%80%9154_%E6%A1%88%E4%BE%8B%E5%8D%A1_%E4%B9%90%E5%87%AF%E6%92%92\">【需内部】案例卡：乐凯撒</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#/doc/90_%E5%86%85%E9%83%A8%E6%BA%90%E6%A1%A3%2F10_%E5%93%81%E7%89%8C%E6%BA%90%E6%A1%A3%2F%E3%80%90%E9%9C%80%E5%86%85%E9%83%A8%E3%80%9155_%E6%A1%88%E4%BE%8B%E5%8D%A1_LINLEE%E6%9E%97%E9%87%8C\">【需内部】案例卡：LINLEE 林里</a></li>\n</ul>\n"
